The vista~
This high-risen mountain ledge hangs over the cliff steadily, strong
enough to hold a crowd of people on top without breaking.  It is a perfect
vista view, looking down over the valley below; the once ripe and rich
grasslands that once lived here all but dead.  From here you can see guess
that carnage that probably happened here in another time, years and years
ago from the looks of it.  The grass is removed mostly from the ground, only
left in small patches where the skirmish didn't get bad.  There are scorched
marks on the ground, and what were large pillars of rock are now boulders
strewn across the field.  
