The Maw of the Beast~
Sights here would take the stomachs of mortals, minus the hardest of
heroes and adventurers, and turn them inside out.  Here is the battlefield,
the true point where the ancients faced the immortals and mortals on the
ground.  Visions, images of the ancients and the heroes are perfectly
crystallized in a blue aura, fighting endlessly for the fate of the world. 
Time and time again creatures and heroes will tear each other apart with
blades and spells, whilst the immortals and ancients stand behind the line,
casting huge spells that no longer exist in any spellbooks.  This is truly a
horribly cursed place.  
